<h2>Ocean View Resort - User Guide</h2>

<hr>

<h3>1. Login</h3>
<p>
  Enter your assigned username and password to access the system.
  Only authorized staff members are allowed to log in.
</p>

<h3>2. Add New Reservation</h3>
<p>
  Click "Add New Reservation" from the dashboard.
  Fill in the guest details and select the room type.
  Choose valid check-in and check-out dates.
  The system will automatically calculate the total bill.
</p>

<h3>3. View Reservation</h3>
<p>
  Click "View Reservation" from the dashboard.
  Enter the Reservation ID to retrieve booking details.
</p>

<h3>4. Print Bill</h3>
<p>
  After creating a reservation, click the "Print Bill" button.
  The invoice page will open.
  Click "Print" to generate a physical copy of the bill.
</p>

<h3>5. Logout</h3>
<p>
  Always click "Logout" after completing your work to ensure system security.
</p>

<hr>

<h3>Important Guidelines</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Ensure check-out date is later than check-in date.</li>
  <li>Reservation ID is generated automatically by the system.</li>
  <li>Do not share your login credentials.</li>
  <li>Verify guest details before confirming reservation.</li>
</ul>

<br>
